The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning algorithms for solving verbal analogies and determining semantic relations in noun-modifier pairs. This suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories, including computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
